^1CHANGES in 3.23:
^4^7Withering Step:
Quality now causes the skill to inflict +0-2 Withered Debuffs the first time each Enemy enters the Area, instead of providing 0-10% increased Effect of Elusive from this Skill.
Blade Vortex:
No longer has 0-10% increased Critical Strike Chance for each blade. It now deals 3 to 5 Physical Damage at gem level 1 (unchanged), scaling up to 140 to 211 at gem level 20 (previously 128 to 191). Quality now provides +0-5% increased Hit Rate for each blade, instead of 0-10% increased Area of Effect.
We also lost our helm enchant :( But it's okay because we scale a bunch of Incrased Skill Effect Duration elsewhere on the tree
Plague Bearer:
Quality now causes Plague Bearer to deal Damage based on an additional +0-4% of Plague Value, instead of providing 0-10% increased Area of Effect.

Skill.label: Withering Step - Use on Bosses (not left click)
Blade Vortex in Empty Gem Sockets to Level
Immortal Call - Use It. Diabled to not inflate EHP
Blade Vortex - Lvl 21 Normal or Lvl 20 Vaal
